title: #76: The Royal Rumble with Eddie Bravo, Pat Miletich and David Clark
description: The guys are excited to welcome from The Conspiracy Farm podcast, Pat Miletich, We Are Superman's, David Clark, and Tin Foil Hat regular, Eddie Bravo for a Round Table, Royal Rumble discussion of conspiracy theories.  We go deep homeboy!
